										goad and <hi rend="italic">Purnaghata</hi> symbols. The five
										toes in front bear a <hi rend="italic">Tri-ratna</hi> on the
										1st finger and the remaining four fingers bear <hi rend="italic">Swastika</hi>
										symbols at the tip. The border has beautifully carved
										foliage motifs. In the corner is carved a mythical crocodile
